<br>
Well, I told myself this morning that I was going to refrain from posting for a few days to let recent events, both guild and RL, settle down a bit.  Today's posts seem to carry an urgency about them such that I feel a need to post some thoughts to consider.<br>
<br>
For those who may not have read this in a while, or even those that have, I encourage you to reread our charter.  There are many things in it that may offer guidance during these times.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://knightsofvalor.freeservers.com/Charter.html">knightsofvalor.freeserver...arter.html</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
<br>
&quot;Each member shall influence the way the guild grows and lives; every voice will be heard and none silenced.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;... live our lives as an example to those around us ...&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;... plant the seeds of hope and serenity wherever we may travel.&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;... his or her actions reflect upon the guild as a whole.&quot;<br>
<br>
<br>
Slaydark and Longbow have a talent beyond that which I possess to express these things in a much more eloquent way so perhaps we might hear some of their thoughts in here as well.  Let truth be your guide and honor your path.<br>
<br>
Safe journeys to all.<br>
